review_blob: Old school. Basic stuff. Still the domain of hardcore drinkers who are set in their ways. No problem with that!

This is an interesting one! If you didnt know any better, you might think you were drinking ICED TEA! Thats not a negative!!! This is definetely one of the most imaginative brews to come along in a long while. Its different for sure and when it comes to trying new things, different is a good thing!
Looking for a new lager to try? If yes, try Kold. Very refreshing and one of the cleanest finishing lagers Ive tasted. Cant go wrong with this one. Buy a case---NOW!
Greatest beer in the world? Yes!
